<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I was wondering if someone can give me a little help here.  I have a 75 or so jewelry skill.  I made a silver star ruby veil (4chr/4dex) and the message said that I could no longer advance my skill making this item.  Well, thinking that this item is now trivial, I decided to make a couple to sell.  The next one that I tried to make failed.  Is it possible to fail on an item that is trivial?  Or are items never trivial? Any help would be appriciated.<p>

Thanks,<br>
Jujucharm</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
